        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the aubergine is cooking, chop your <strong>creamed coconut </strong>roughly (if required!)</p><p>Add your <strong>basmati rice</strong>, <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong> and 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> to a pot with a lid and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 10-12 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked, then remove from the heat and keep covered until later</p>",
