      "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>pineapple</strong> (save the juice!) and chop finely</p><p>Peel and finely chop your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Cut your<strong> red chilli[es]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
