    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the<strong> chopped pineapple</strong>,<strong> chopped shallot</strong>,<strong> chopped chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>chopped coriander </strong>in a bowl</p><p>Add the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s] </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>pineapple salsa</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
