    {
      "instruction": "<p>After an initial 20 min, remove the tray[s] from the oven and spoon the <strong>spiced glaze </strong>over the <strong>softened aubergine</strong></p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for a further 8-10 min or until caramelised – this is your <strong>Caribbean-style aubergine</strong></p><p>While the aubergine is cooking, drain and rinse your <strong>black beans</strong></p>",
