    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is cooked, return it to a medium heat with the<strong> drained black beans</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until the beans are warmed through – this is your<strong> coconut rice & beans</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
